%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor ADMIN as Admin

participant UI as Governance Workspace UI
participant BFF as Governance BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant GOV as Governance Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

ADMIN->>UI: Open Project Governance Definitions
UI->>BFF: Load governance workspace
BFF->>GOV: Get archetype workspace
%%ORCH->>GOV: Fetch archetype list
GOV->>READDB: Query governance_archetype
READDB-->>GOV: Archetype records
GOV-->>BFF: Aggregated workspace
BFF-->>UI: Show archetype list / empty state

ADMIN->>UI: Click Add Archetype
UI->>BFF: Create archetype draft
BFF->>ORCH: Start archetype draft flow
ORCH->>GOV: Create archetype draft
GOV->>PRIMARYDB: Insert governance_archetype(status=Draft)
GOV->>PRIMARYDB: Insert status history
GOV-->>ORCH: Draft created
ORCH-->>BFF: Success
BFF-->>UI: Open Archetype Details
